### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### List ingredients
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ingredients

### Create chicken breast
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ingredients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Chicken Breast, raw",
    "macroBasis": "RAW",
    "proteinPer100g": 31.0,
    "carbsPer100g": 0.0,
    "fatPer100g": 3.6,
    "kcalPer100g": 165.0,
    "notes": "From Cronometer Data"
}

### Get chicken breast
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ingredients/1


### Create prep session
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prep-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionDate": "2026-07-20",
  "notes": "Sunday chicken prep"
}

### Add chicken batch to session (use session id from above)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/prep-sessions/1/batches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredient": { "id": 1 },
  "rawWeightG": 2146,
  "cookedWeightG": 1600
}

### Read session back with batches
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prep-sessions/1